type: Tutorial Step - To Infinity and Beyond

definition.text: If you have submitted a review then you are ready to go. We will be using the app.contribute command again to finish submitting your profile.

paragraphs.text: Go to the docs panel and type the following command into the search bar:
app.contribute This is my first submission of User Profile [add your name here]

If everything is set up correctly you should see the message appear that your pull request has been submitted.  This means that your profile has been sent to the main Superalgos repository and will be automatically merged in just a few minutes!
